title: AirMagnet
extract: AirMagnet Survey is an Enterprise level wireless site survey software solution used by network professionals for mapping, planning and designing 802.11n/a/b/g/ac wireless LANs for optimal performance, security and compliance.
extract_html: AirMagnet Survey is an Enterprise level wireless site survey software solution used by network professionals for mapping, planning and designing 802.11n/a/b/g/ac wireless LANs for optimal performance, security and compliance.
